ysmal-thoughts|website=[[The Skinny (magazine)|The Skinny]]|publisher=Radge Media|accessdate=June 16, 2017|date=June 12, 2017}}</ref>\n|rev8      = ''[[Under the Radar (magazine)|Under the Radar]]''\n|rev8Score = {{rating|5.5|10}}<ref name=\"UTR\">{{cite web|last1=Mayne|first1=Steven|title=The Drums: \"Abysmal Thoughts\"|url=http://www.undertheradarmag.com/reviews/the_drums_abysmal_thoughts/|website=[[Under the Radar (magazine)|Under the Radar]]|publisher=UTR|accessdate=June 16, 2017|date=June 16, 2017}}</ref>\n}}\n\n'''''Abysmal Thoughts''''' is the fourth studio album by New York City [[surf rock]] band [[The Drums]]. The album was released on June 16, 2017, through [[Anti- (record label)|ANTI-]].\n\nThe album was preceded by the single, \"Blood Under My Belt.\"<ref name=\"Blood Under My Belt\"/>\n\n== Track listing ==\n{{Track listing\n| all_writing     = \n| total_length    = 49:05\n| title1  = Mirror\n| length1 = 4:04\n| title2  = I\u2019ll Fight for Your Life\n| length2 = 3:51\n| title3  = Blood Under My Belt\n| length3 = 3:48\n| title4  = Heart Basel\n| length4 = 4:43\n| title5  = Shoot the Sun Down\n| length5 = 3:36\n| title6  = Head of the Horse\n| length6 = 4:38\n| title7  = Under the Ice\n| length7 = 3:41\n| title8  = Are U Fucked\n| length8 = 3:59\n| title9  = Your Tenderness\n| length9 = 4:57\n| title10  = Rich Kids\n| length10 = 3:07\n| title11  = If All We Share (Means Nothing)\n| length11 = 3:50\n| title12  = Abysmal Thoughts\n| length12 = 4:51\n}}\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2017)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br /> position\n|-\n{{album chart|Wallonia|157|artist=The Drums|album=Abysmal Thoughts|rowheader=true|accessdate=June 30, 2017}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|UK [[UK Independent Singles and Albums Charts|Independent Albums]] ([[Official Charts Company|OCC]])<ref>[http://www.officialcharts.com/charts/independent-albums-chart/20170623/131/ \"Official Independent Albums Chart Top 50\"]. [[Official Charts Company]]. June 23 \u2013 29, 2017. Retrieved February 23, 2018.</ref>\n|48\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US [[Heatseekers Albums]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref>[https://www.billboard.com/music/The-Drums/chart-history/heatseekers-albums/song/1030883 \"The Drums Abysmal Thoughts Chart History\"]. ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' [[Heatseekers Albums]]. Retrieved February 23, 2018.</ref>\n| 5\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US [[Independent Albums]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref>[https://www.billboard.com/music/the-drums/chart-history/independent-albums/song/1030883 \"The Drums Abysmal Thoughts Chart History\"]. ''Billboard'' [[Independent Albums]]. Retrieved February 23, 2018.</ref>\n|24\n|}\n\n== Personnel ==\n* Producer/Musician: Jonathan Pierce\n* Engineer/Mixer: Jonathan Schenke\n* Mastering: Joe LaPorta\n* Management: Andrew Mishko\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n{{The Drums}}\n\n[[Category:2017 albums]]\n[[Category:The Drums albums]]\n[[Category:Anti- (record label) albums]]\n\n{{2010s-indie-pop-album-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Abysmal Thoughts\n| type       = studio\n| artist     = [[The Drums]]\n| cover      = Drumsat.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = June 16, 2017\n| recorded   =\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Indie pop]], [[surf rock]]\n| length     = 49:05\n| label      = [[Anti- (record label)|ANTI-]]\n| producer   =\n| prev_title = [[Encyclopedia (album)|Encyclopedia]]\n| prev_year  = 2014\n| next_title = [[Brutalism (The Drums album)|Brutalism]]\n| next_year  = 2019\n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Abysmal Thoughts\n | type        = studio\n | single1     = Blood Under My Belt\n | single1date = March 1, 2017<ref name=\"Blood Under My Belt\">{{cite web|last1=Hogan|first1=Marc|title=\"Blood Under My Belt\" Review|url=http://pitchfork.com/reviews/tracks/18775-the-drums-blood-under-my-belt/|website=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]|publishe