mal-thoughts-anti-records/|website=God Is In the TV|publisher=godisinthetvzine.co.uk|accessdate=June 16, 2017|date=June 12, 2017}}</ref>\n|rev5      = ''[[Loud and Quiet]]''\n|rev5Score = 7/10<ref name=\"L&Q\">{{cite web|last1=Beswick|first1=Katie|title=The Drums - Abysmal Thoughts|url=http://www.loudandquiet.com/reviews/drums-abysmal-thoughts/|website=[[Loud and Quiet]]|publisher=Stubbs Media|accessdate=June 16, 2017}}</ref>\n|rev6      = ''[[Paste (magazine)|Paste]]''\n|rev6Score = 8.1/10<ref name=\"Paste\">{{cite web|last1=Cudmore|first1=Libby|title=The Drums: Abysmal Thoughts Review|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2017/06/the-drums-abysmal-thoughts-review.html|website=[[Paste (magazine)|Paste]]|publisher=[[Wolfgang's Vault]]|accessdate=June 16, 2017|date=June 14, 2017}}</ref>\n|rev7      = [[The Skinny (magazine)|The Skinny]]\n|rev7Score = {{rating|3|5}}<ref name=\"Skinny\">{{cite web|last1=Atcheson|first1=Alastair|title=The Drums - Abysmal Thoughts album review|url=http://www.theskinny.co.uk/music/reviews/albums/the-drums-abysmal-thoughts|website=[[The Skinny (magazine)|The Skinny]]|publisher=Radge Media|accessdate=June 16, 2017|date=June 12, 2017}}</ref>\n|rev8      = ''[[Under the Radar (magazine)|Under the Radar]]''\n|rev8Score = {{rating|5.5|10}}<ref name=\"UTR\">{{cite web|last1=Mayne|first1=Steven|title=The Drums: \"Abysmal Thoughts\"|url=http://www.undertheradarmag.com/reviews/the_drums_abysmal_thoughts/|website=[[Under the Radar (magazine)|Under the Radar]]|publisher=UTR|accessdate=June 16, 2017|date=June 16, 2017}}</ref>\n}}\n\n'''''Abysmal Thoughts''''' is the fourth studio album by New York City [[surf rock]] band, [[The Drums]]. The album was released on June 16, 2017 through [[Anti- (record label)|ANTI-]].\n\nThe album was preceded by the lead single, \"Blood Under My Belt\".<ref name=\"Blood Under My Belt\"/>\n\n== Track listing ==\n{{Track listing\n| all_writing     = \n| total_length    = 49:05\n| title1  = Mirror\n| length1 = 4:04\n|